'From Squeak2.9alpha of 13 June 2000 [latest update: #2915] on 12 November 2000 at 5:46:37 pm'!"Change Set:		241NewSymbolTable3-sqrDate:			23 August 2000Author:			Andres ValloudMore..."!!Character methodsFor: 'converting' stamp: 'SqR 8/23/2000 16:19'!asSymbol 	"Answer a Symbol consisting of the receiver as the only element."	^Symbol intern: self asString! !!Scanner methodsFor: 'multi-character scans' stamp: 'SqR 8/23/2000 16:20'!xBinary	tokenType _ #binary.	token _ self step asSymbol.	[(typeTable at: hereChar asciiValue) = #xBinary and: [hereChar ~= $-]]		whileTrue: [token _ (token , (String with: self step)) asSymbol]! !!Symbol class methodsFor: 'class initialization' stamp: 'SqR 8/23/2000 16:15'!initialize	"Symbol initialize"	SymbolTable _ WeakSet withAll: self allInstances! !Symbol initialize!Symbol class removeSelector: #initializeNewSymbolTable!"Postscript:"Symbol initialize.Symbol class removeSelector: #initializeNewSymbolTable!